Interface I_XMLable

      • toXML_

        java.lang.StringBuilder toXML_​(java.lang.StringBuilder... instream)
        Generates an XML representation of the contents of this object. This representation is for display purposes only, not as a data structure.
        Parameters:
        instream - - any stream to inject into this one as appropriate. Whether this is required, prohibited, or optional depends on the method implementation. If present, only one element is allowed.
        Returns:
        the representation
